Titolo: Darkstalkers 3

Anno: 1997

Descrizione: Darkstalkers 3, known in Japan as Vampire Savior: The Lord of Vampire (ヴァンパイア セイヴァー ザ ロード オブ ヴァンパイアズ, Vanpaia Seivā Za Rōdo Obu Vanpaiazu), is the second sequel in the Darkstalkers series of fighting games by Capcom, originally released in arcades in 1997. This third installment centers around a demonic nobleman from Makai named Jedah Dohma, who creates a pocket dimension named Majigen where he tries to bring in souls to help nourish his new world. It was critically and commercially well-received, and home versions were released for the PlayStation and Saturn.

Genere: Fighting 

Valutazione: N/A
